responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "1AF263A24A769F0EBB26E79C781F4342", "Sir Pitt did don his black armor and raven cloak and became one with the night. Within the shadow realm he hunted the midnight killer, the Moonstalker. His bravery saw the eradication of the ferocious beast of the midnight moors.")
